### Get all boards
GET http://localhost:8080/api/boards

###

### Get board by id 
GET http://localhost:8080/api/boards/1

###

### Get board details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/boards/1/details

###

### Create board
POST http://localhost:8080/api/boards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Website Redesign"
}

###

### Update board 
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/boards/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Website Redesign Updated"
}

###

### Get all columns
GET http://localhost:8080/api/column

###

### Get column by id 
GET http://localhost:8080/api/column/1

###

### Create column
POST http://localhost:8080/api/column
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Todo",
  "boardId": 1
}

###

### Update column 
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/column/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "In Progress",
  "boardId": 1
}

###

### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks

###

### Get task by id 
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1

###

### Create task !!
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Create wireframes",
  "description": "Design the landing page",
  "columnId": 1
}

###

### Update task !!
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Create wireframes updated",
  "description": "Revise landing page draft",
  "columnId": 2
}

###